description: Product Description Best House Aluminium Roasting,Baking Tray Best House Premium Quality Aluminum Foil Pans Best House Disposable Catering Pans are designed to be multifunctional - you can bake, serve, display, and store all in one dish! Our foil pans have a high gauge and full curl rim for sturdiness and durability. Cook dishes without the worry of the pans breaking or ripping. Our foil trays are easily stackable to help reduce storage space. Cleanup is even easier - simply toss when you’re done! Great for catering, buffets, barbecues, weddings, and more! Sturdy Foil Construction High Gauge Rolled-Rim Stackable Freezer-Safe Oven-Safe OVEN SAFE Our pans are thermally conductive making them perfect for baking cakes, brownies, cinnamon rolls, lasagna, mac n cheese, casseroles, and more! FREEZER SAFE Our pans freezer safe, allowing you to store leftovers in the fridge. They're also great for meal-prep. Freeze dishes until you’re ready to cook and/or serve. EASY TO USE Our foil pans make cleanup a breeze - just toss 'em in the trash when you're done! Perfect for catering, restaurants, bake sales, barbecues, and more! EASY TO CARRY Our aluminum foil pans are a convenient way to transport and serve meals anywhere, anytime
